14:35.194 --> 14:38.663
MAN 1: Hey, everybody,
Wilfred's back!

14:38.664 --> 14:41.165
Pick me!
I just want to die!

14:41.166 --> 14:45.670
WOMAN: No, no! I'm more
tumor than person! Pick me!

14:45.671 --> 14:47.338
MR. HELMS:
I'll suck your dick!

14:47.339 --> 14:50.107
That's a good pitch,
but I want to hear others.

14:50.108 --> 14:52.142
Ah... you.

14:52.143 --> 14:55.312
Skeletor. Why do you
deserve to die?

14:55.313 --> 14:59.684
You think you smart, but I
figure out what you are doing!

14:59.685 --> 15:01.253
Your dog be distracting
everybody

15:01.254 --> 15:03.455
so you can steal our medicines!

15:03.456 --> 15:06.058
Zip it, Ruby.
I checked the records.

15:06.059 --> 15:10.063
Your key card is the only one
accessing the drug closet.

15:10.064 --> 15:11.764
So if anything's missing,
it's on you!

15:11.765 --> 15:13.633
You'll be sorry.

15:13.634 --> 15:17.937
Soon, everybody be sorry!

15:17.938 --> 15:19.572
(panting)

15:19.573 --> 15:22.141
Don't worry, I'll deal
with the nurse.

15:22.142 --> 15:24.677
I'll make her see the light.
What are you gonna...?

15:24.678 --> 15:28.014
Hey, are you ready
for your close-up?

15:28.015 --> 15:32.352
Okay. All right, Ryan,
we're almost ready. You nervous?

15:32.353 --> 15:36.189
I'm just trying to figure out
how the hell I got here.

15:36.190 --> 15:37.724
Look, just be yourself.

15:37.725 --> 15:39.660
You know, the one thing that
being in front

15:39.661 --> 15:41.128
of the camera
has taught me is that

15:41.129 --> 15:42.363
some people are gonna
like you,

15:42.364 --> 15:43.764
and some people
are gonna hate you.

15:43.765 --> 15:45.499
But if you worry
about what other people think,

15:45.500 --> 15:47.301
you'll just drive
yourself crazy.

15:47.302 --> 15:49.103
You'll be great.

15:49.104 --> 15:51.072
So I'm just gonna start
by asking you a few questions.

15:51.073 --> 15:52.240
(loud thud)

15:52.241 --> 15:54.742
Oh, my God!

15:54.743 --> 15:56.811
It's Ruby.

15:59.881 --> 16:01.615
RYAN:
Wilfred!

16:03.118 --> 16:05.853
Oh, my God,
you did it!

16:05.854 --> 16:08.189
You really did it!

16:08.190 --> 16:11.525
Whatever I did, I did
for the both of us.

16:11.526 --> 16:14.161
No! I never wanted this!

16:14.162 --> 16:16.030
Tell me something,
Ryan.

16:16.031 --> 16:18.165
When those pathetic bags
of bones

16:18.166 --> 16:20.268
down there fall to their knees

16:20.269 --> 16:24.505
and pray for death, who do you
think they're praying to?

16:24.506 --> 16:26.574
Me! That's who.

16:26.575 --> 16:28.442
You've lost your mind.

16:28.443 --> 16:30.744
It's like you've got
some kind of God complex!

16:30.745 --> 16:32.847
I'll let you in on
a little secret, Ryan.

16:32.848 --> 16:35.282
I haven't got a God complex.

16:35.283 --> 16:40.121
<i>I am God! Thunder!</i>

16:40.122 --> 16:41.789
How did you do that?!

16:41.790 --> 16:44.158
Lucky coincidence!

16:44.159 --> 16:46.226
You've got it wrong, Wilfred...

16:46.227 --> 16:48.829
and so did I!

16:48.830 --> 16:50.931
I don't care
what other people think!

16:50.932 --> 16:54.234
The only thing that matters
is how I feel about myself!

16:54.235 --> 16:57.938
Well, it's a little late
for that.

16:57.939 --> 16:59.807
I won't let you get away
with this.

16:59.808 --> 17:02.543
Stay out of my way...

17:02.544 --> 17:07.414
or the next bed I curl up in
might be yours.

17:07.415 --> 17:09.715
No!

17:09.717 --> 17:11.752
I have something to say!

17:11.752 --> 17:13.720
You're making
a big mistake, Ryan.

17:13.721 --> 17:16.757
I don't care. I can't let this
go on any longer.

17:16.758 --> 17:18.492
Hey, look, Ruby left
a suicide note.

17:18.493 --> 17:19.661
She did?

17:21.631 --> 17:25.435
Are you sure it's in
human handwriting?

17:25.435 --> 17:26.935
I swear
that's not a racial thing.

17:26.936 --> 17:29.373
Look, Ryan, I hate
to do this,

17:29.374 --> 17:32.743
but I think there's
a bigger story here
than you and Wilfred.

17:32.744 --> 17:34.211
No, no, no, there's
no story here.

17:34.212 --> 17:36.446
We don't need this
kind of publicity.

17:36.447 --> 17:38.615
I'm sorry, but you've got
a rogue nurse who

17:38.616 --> 17:40.751
apparently stole
huge amounts of drugs
and then killed herself

17:40.752 --> 17:43.121
out of guilt.
This is a pretty
juicy exclusive.

17:43.122 --> 17:45.890
This hospice is struggling
as it is.

17:45.891 --> 17:47.859
This could shut us down.

17:47.860 --> 17:49.894
I know, and I feel
really, really badly.

17:50.602 --> 17:51.635
We're going live.

17:56.358 --> 18:01.427
You know, you had me
worried back there
at the hospice.

18:01.428 --> 18:05.331
You-you didn't actually
kill anyone, did you?

18:05.332 --> 18:07.567
No! Ryan!

18:11.338 --> 18:14.406
Except for the old lady.
I definitely killed her.

18:14.407 --> 18:15.774
Gotcha.

18:15.775 --> 18:17.176
(sighs)

18:17.177 --> 18:19.879
But seriously,
I did.

18:19.880 --> 18:23.049
Ah-ha! I'm kidding!

18:23.050 --> 18:25.351
Wait. You're kidding
that you did,

18:25.352 --> 18:27.586
or you're kidding
that you didn't?

18:29.589 --> 18:33.125
Okay, Ryan, I... I really don't
want you to get mad here,

18:33.126 --> 18:36.361
but I'm guilty...

18:36.362 --> 18:38.863
of being charming.

18:40.433 --> 18:42.100
And killing
an old lady.

18:42.101 --> 18:44.469
With kindness!

18:44.470 --> 18:45.771
And a pillow.

18:45.772 --> 18:47.973
Just kidding!

18:50.710 --> 18:52.978
Or am I?

19:00.653 --> 19:02.054
Nice kid.

19:02.055 --> 19:04.890
That is so typical
of Western thinking:

19:04.891 --> 19:06.659
If you can't see it
for yourself,

19:06.660 --> 19:08.160
it doesn't exist.

19:08.161 --> 19:10.129
I've actually got
many, many magical powers

19:10.130 --> 19:11.897
that would blow your mind.

19:11.898 --> 19:14.099
Like what?

19:14.100 --> 19:17.736
Off the top of my head,
I can make you disappear.

19:17.737 --> 19:20.005
(scoffs) Prove it.

19:20.006 --> 19:21.840
Make me disappear.

19:21.841 --> 19:23.008
Okay.

19:24.944 --> 19:27.846
Look deeply
into my eyes.

19:27.847 --> 19:31.216
Now you... you've really got
to concentrate here, okay?

19:31.217 --> 19:35.453
So, we're breathing
deeply in through the nose

19:35.454 --> 19:38.956
and out through
the mouth.

19:38.957 --> 19:40.925
Focus.

19:45.798 --> 19:47.700
Now one big one.

19:49.936 --> 19:53.873
Oh! Oh, God!

19:53.874 --> 19:56.510
And just like that, he's gone.

